fcitx: fcitx (input method for simplified Chinese)
fcitx: 
fcitx: fcitx stands for Free Chinese Input Toy of X, an input method for Linux. 
fcitx: To be more precise, fctix is a collection of Simplified Chinese input 
fcitx: methods based on XIM (X Input Method), including WuBi, PinYin, and 
fcitx: QuWei, and it is distributed under GPL. It is the descendent of gWuBi.
fcitx: 
